## 9. Архитектурный скелет (визуальный пример)

```html
<!-- Tech label в углу structural panel -->
<div class="pi-corner-marks hairline p-stack-lg relative">
  <span class="pi-tech-label absolute top-2 right-2">REF: 80.4.2</span>
  <h3 class="font-title-sm mb-stack-sm">Architectural Edition</h3>
  <p class="text-body-sm text-muted-foreground">UI Kit Showcase</p>
</div>

<!-- Dashed empty state -->
<div class="pi-dashed-panel p-stack-lg text-center">
  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-muted-foreground">folder_open</span>
  <h3 class="font-title-sm mt-stack-md">No Active Projects</h3>
  <p class="text-body-sm text-muted-foreground">Start a new query to see data here.</p>
</div>

<!-- Tabular-nums для numeric table cell -->
<td class="px-gutter font-data-mono text-body-sm tabular-nums">TX-8092</td>
<td class="px-gutter font-data-mono tabular-nums text-right">99.98%</td>
```

